OL,3,CEarly penalty goal for England in
OL,4,Copening World Cup game against Croatia
OL,6,FHarry Kane has scored England's first
OL,7,Fgoal in the 11th minute of their
OL,8,Fopening match against Croatia
OL,10,FDespite it looking like the early
OL,11,Fpenalty opportunity had been missed,
OL,12,FKane was given a second shot after a
OL,13,FVAR decision.
OL,15,FHarry Kane did not miss a second time.
OL,17,FEngland began their Fifa World Cup
OL,18,F2026 campaign this evening, playing
OL,19,Ffellow European heavyweights Croatia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
