OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781858896
OL,3,CEarly penalty goal for England in
OL,4,Copening World Cup game against Croatia
OL,6,FRanked 11th in the world, Croatia has
OL,7,Fbeen a thorn in England's side in
OL,8,Fprevious years, most famously beating
OL,9,Fthem in the semi-finals of the 2018
OL,10,FWorld Cup.
OL,12,FThe game kicked off at 3pm local time
OL,13,F(9pm BST) at Dallas Stadium in Texas,
OL,14,Fusually home to the NFL's Dallas
OL,15,FCowboys.
OL,17,FToday, Thomas Tuchel's England side
OL,18,Fare hoping to secure the top spot in
OL,19,FGroup L, which also includes Ghana and
OL,20,FPanama.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
