PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781858896
OL,3,CEarly penalty goal for England in
OL,4,Copening World Cup game against Croatia
OL,6,FBukayo Saka and Marcus Rashford both
OL,7,Fbegin Wednesday's game on the bench,
OL,8,Fafter Saka missed some training due to
OL,9,Fan Achilles injury. Meanwhile, Anthony
OL,10,FGordon will be starting ahead of
OL,11,FRashford.
OL,13,FSome 15,000 optimistic England fans
OL,14,Fmade the journey to the States in
OL,15,Fsupport of the Three Lions.
OL,17,FDespite the Texas heat, England fans
OL,18,Fqueued outside the stadium dressed up
OL,19,Fin face paint and football shirts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
