OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781858896
OL,3,CEarly penalty goal for England in
OL,4,Copening World Cup game against Croatia
OL,6,FCommenting on England's chances for
OL,7,Fthe tournament, one fan said: "I have
OL,8,Ffull faith. This is it. This is the
OL,9,Ftime we're going to win".
OL,11,FAhead of the match, the Prince of
OL,12,FWales took to social media to wish the
OL,13,Fteam luck.
OL,15,FHe said: "Good luck to England ahead
OL,16,Fof their first World Cup group match
OL,17,Ftonight! Here's to a great tournament
OL,18,Fahead."
